#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.206"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.206:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.206:0.2"
msgid "21. Sappurisavagga"
msgstr "21. A Good Person"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: chaṭṭhasappurisasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.206:0.3"
msgid "206. Dasamaggasutta"
msgstr "206. The Path with Ten Factors"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.206:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Asappurisañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi, asappurisena asappurisatarañca;"
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you a bad person and a worse person,"

msgctxt "an4.206:1.2"
msgid "sappurisañca, sappurisena sappurisatarañca. Taṃ suṇātha … pe …."
msgstr "a good person and a better person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.222"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.206:2.1"
msgid "“Katamo ca, bhikkhave, asappuriso?"
msgstr "And what is a bad person?"

msgctxt "an4.206:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco micchādiṭṭhiko hoti … pe … micchāñāṇī hoti, "
"micchāvimutti hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has wrong view, wrong thought, wrong speech, wrong action, "
"wrong livelihood, wrong effort, wrong mindfulness, wrong immersion, wrong "
"knowledge, and wrong freedom."

msgctxt "an4.206:2.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asappuriso."
msgstr "This is called a bad person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.206:3.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, asappurisena asappurisataro?"
msgstr "And what is a worse person?"

msgctxt "an4.206:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco attanā ca micchādiṭṭhiko hoti, parañca "
"micchādiṭṭhiyā samādapeti … pe … attanā ca micchāñāṇī hoti, parañca "
"micchāñāṇe samādapeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has wrong view, wrong thought, wrong speech, wrong action, "
"wrong livelihood, wrong effort, wrong mindfulness, wrong immersion, wrong "
"knowledge, and wrong freedom. And they encourage others in these same "
"qualities."

msgctxt "an4.206:3.3"
msgid "attanā ca micchāvimutti hoti, parañca micchāvimuttiyā samādapeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.206:3.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asappurisena asappurisataro."
msgstr "This is called a worse person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.206:4.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, sappuriso?"
msgstr "And what is a good person?"

msgctxt "an4.206:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco sammādiṭṭhiko hoti … pe … sammāñāṇī hoti, "
"sammāvimutti hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has right view, right thought, right speech, right action, "
"right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, right immersion, right "
"knowledge, and right freedom."

msgctxt "an4.206:4.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sappuriso."
msgstr "This is called a good person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.206:5.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, sappurisena sappurisataro?"
msgstr "And what is a better person?"

msgctxt "an4.206:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco attanā ca sammādiṭṭhiko hoti, parañca sammādiṭṭhiyā "
"samādapeti … pe … attanā ca sammāñāṇī hoti, parañca sammāñāṇe samādapeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has right view, right thought, right speech, right action, "
"right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, right immersion, right "
"knowledge, and right freedom. And they encourage others in these same "
"qualities."

msgctxt "an4.206:5.3"
msgid "attanā ca sammāvimutti hoti, parañca sammāvimuttiyā samādapeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.206:5.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sappurisena sappurisataro”ti."
msgstr "This is called a better person.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.206:5.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
